1. Ne znam kako da *slomim* led na ulici. (I don't know how to *break* the ice on the street.)
2. Zbog finansijskih problema, firma je *slomljena*. (Due to financial problems, the company is *broken*.)
3. Uspeli su da *slome* otpor neprijatelja. (They managed to *break* the resistance of the enemy.)
4. Moram da pazim da ne *slomim* novu čašu. (I have to be careful not to *break* the new glass.)
5. Kada je čuo loše vesti, *slomio* se i počeo da plače. (When he heard the bad news, he *broke* down and started to cry.)
6. Treba da *slomimo* led i da krenemo. (We need to *break* the ice and get started.)
7. Povreda mu je *slomila* karijeru. (The injury *broke* his career.)
8. Nadao se da će dobiti posao, ali je bio *slomljen* kada su ga odbili. (He hoped to get the job, but he was *broken* when they turned him down.)
9. Moramo *slomiti* loše navike i početi da vodimo zdraviji život. (We need to *break* bad habits and start living healthier.)
10. Nakon dugog razmišljanja, *slomio* je nerešivu dilemu. (After long thinking, he *resolved* the unsolvable dilemma.)